@startuml
title Viaverse Request Creation — Use Case Diagram
left to right direction

actor "Requester\nREQUEST_WORK" as Requester
actor "AI Assistant" as AI
actor "Media Service" as Media
actor "Map Provider" as Maps

rectangle "Service Request Creation Boundary" {
  usecase "Open Create sheet" as Open
  usecase "Select\nRequest a service" as Select
  usecase "Describe need" as Describe
  usecase "Get AI category suggestion" as AiCategory
  usecase "Confirm category\nand subcategory" as ConfirmCategory
  usecase "Choose budget mode\nand range" as Budget
  usecase "Set location\nand service area" as Location
  usecase "Set preferred time\nand urgency" as Time
  usecase "Attach images/videos" as AttachMedia
  usecase "Set visibility\nand matching rules" as Visibility
  usecase "Save draft" as Draft
  usecase "Preview request" as Preview
  usecase "Publish request" as Publish
  usecase "Emit events\nServiceRequestPublished\nMatchingRequested" as Events
}

Requester --> Open
Open --> Select
Select --> Describe
Describe ..> AiCategory : <<include>>
AiCategory --> ConfirmCategory : editable suggestion
ConfirmCategory --> Budget
Budget --> Location
Location --> Time
Time --> AttachMedia
AttachMedia --> Visibility
Visibility --> Draft : draft path
Visibility --> Preview : publish path
Preview --> Publish
Publish --> Events : outbox

AI --> AiCategory : category + text hints
AI --> Budget : budget guidance
Media --> AttachMedia : upload refs
Maps --> Location : geocode / area

note bottom
Rules:
- Request can stay DRAFT until publish
- AI suggestions are editable
- Exact address is private
- Publish writes source-of-truth + outbox events
end note
@enduml
